Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我也很害怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でも...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是...
