Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.13,Default CN,,0,0,0,,拜託 保倫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,変身するポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,變身吧！
