Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:46.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,White
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今度こそ最後だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們死到臨頭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,全然  歯が立たない...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,完全不是他的對手...
